# Design system (Figma)

- **Source file:** [Magali-Solle](https://www.figma.com/design/FeF5ES2xRY75wBP8gFjOVr/Magali-Solle) — single source of truth for colors and button tokens.
- **Tokens:** `app/globals.css` (`@theme` + `:root`-style variables under `--tracking-button`, `--radius-button-*`, `--padding-button-*`, `--color-*`). When Figma Variables change, update those values there first.
- **Buttons:** Do not hand-roll long Tailwind strings for buttons. Use:
  - `btn-primary` — filled pill (nav Work / About)
  - `btn-secondary-soft` — ghost hero CTA
  - `btn-outline-footer` — outline on dark footer
  - `btn-tertiary` — case study row link + icon
- New buttons should extend these classes or add a variant in `@layer components` in `globals.css` using the same CSS variables.
